Tribal violence in Darfur, Sudan, kills at least 163 people and displaces 50,000 others. (AllAfrica.com) (Reuters)Ousted President Viktor Yanukovich, whose whereabouts remained unknown before he turned up in Russia, issues a statement saying that he is still the legitimate president and "ready to fight to the end" to fulfill his deal with the opposition. (USA Today)A bomb kills three Pakistan Army soldiers and injures four others in the restive province of Balochistan. (Al-Arabiya)